About us
We have an amazing number of very talented campers who enjoy spending their time creating new classes or new activities, such as Scrapbooking, Beanie Bags, and MORE–You can be as busy as you want to be!
Our campers are what make Shady Oaks such a GREAT place to spend the winter, and they return year after year, not only because of what we offer, but because the atmosphere is “family.”
